cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file."
title: "microstructure-tpw: Ocean microstructure turbulence processing (TKE dissipation and chi)"
abstract: >-
  Python tools for reading Rockland Scientific microprofiler data (VMP and
  MicroRider) and computing the rate of dissipation of turbulent kinetic energy
  (epsilon) and the rate of dissipation of thermal variance (chi) from shear
  probes and FP07 fast thermistors.
type: software
authors:
